{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_017mgCWbgqnEQk9yq1dYKH95","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All acceptance criteria are met. Here is a summary of everything created:\n\n---\n\n## US-001 Complete: Package Scaffolding\n\n### Files Created\n\n**`/Users/chrisarter/Documents/projects/policy-engine/composer.json`**\n- `name: \"dynamik-dev/laravel-policy-engine\"`, `type: \"library\"`\n- PHP `^8.4`, Laravel `^11.0|^12.0` (via illuminate packages)\n- Dev deps: `pestphp/pest`, `pestphp/pest-plugin-laravel`, `orchestra/testbench`, `laravel/pint`\n- PSR-4 autoload: `DynamikDev\\\\PolicyEngine\\\\` to `src/`\n- PSR-4 autoload-dev: `DynamikDev\\\\PolicyEngine\\\\Tests\\\\` to `tests/`\n- `extra.laravel.providers` includes `PolicyEngineServiceProvider`\n\n**`/Users/chrisarter/Documents/projects/policy-engine/src/PolicyEngineServiceProvider.php`**\n```php\nclass PolicyEngineServiceProvider extends ServiceProvider\n{\n    public function register(): void\n    {\n        $this->mergeConfigFrom(__DIR__ . '/../config/policy-engine.php', 'policy-engine');\n    }\n\n    public function boot(): void\n    {\n        if ($this->app->runningInConsole()) {\n            $this->publishes([\n                __DIR__ . '/../config/policy-engine.php' => config_path('policy-engine.php'),\n            ], 'policy-engine-config');\n        }\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**`/Users/chrisarter/Documents/projects/policy-engine/config/policy-engine.php`** -- exact config array as specified in acceptance criteria.\n\n**`/Users/chrisarter/Documents/projects/policy-engine/phpunit.xml`** -- configured with `tests/Feature` suite and `src/` source coverage.\n\n**`/Users/chrisarter/Documents/projects/policy-engine/tests/Pest.php`** -- binds `TestCase` for Feature tests.\n\n**`/Users/chrisarter/Documents/projects/policy-engine/tests/TestCase.php`** -- extends `Orchestra\\Testbench\\TestCase`, registers `PolicyEngineServiceProvider`.\n\n### Directory Structure (all