{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01CUvyr2eRpve5Lt5FPm5nS4","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# Policy Engine Package - Agent Memory\n     2→\n     3→## Package Identity\n     4→- **Name:** `dynamik-dev/laravel-policy-engine`\n     5→- **Type:** Laravel library package (NOT an application)\n     6→- **Namespace:** `DynamikDev\\PolicyEngine\\`\n     7→- **PHP:** ^8.4, **Laravel:** ^11.0|^12.0\n     8→\n     9→## Directory Structure\n    10→- `src/` - Main source (PSR-4: `DynamikDev\\PolicyEngine\\`)\n    11→- `src/Contracts/`, `src/Stores/`, `src/Models/`, `src/Concerns/`, `src/Events/`\n    12→- `src/Facades/`, `src/Middleware/`, `src/Commands/`, `src/DTOs/`, `src/Documents/`\n    13→- `config/policy-engine.php` - Package config\n    14→- `tests/` - PSR-4: `DynamikDev\\PolicyEngine\\Tests\\`\n    15→- `tests/Feature/` - Feature tests (Pest)\n    16→\n    17→## Testing Setup\n    18→- **Pest 3** with `pestphp/pest-plugin-laravel`\n    19→- **Orchestra Testbench 9/10** for Laravel package testing context\n    20→- Base `tests/TestCase.php` extends `Orchestra\\Testbench\\TestCase`\n    21→- `tests/Pest.php` binds `TestCase` for Feature tests\n    22→- **Pint** added as dev dependency for formatting\n    23→\n    24→## Key Files\n    25→- `/src/PolicyEngineServiceProvider.php` - Merges config, publishes under `policy-engine-config` tag\n    26→- `/config/policy-engine.php` - cache, protect_system_roles, log_denials, explain, document_format\n    27→- `/phpunit.xml` - Feature test suite only, source coverage on `src/`\n    28→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01QthMt2vfnYoL6TihTPiTjx","session_id":"ce4d2e8c-11e0-48e3-8ef5-8ea123e4d07a","uuid":"71d42d3a-aeb6-4d13-8634-b5bdcf051bea"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01VZ3evyXheEgYGWhrQFQ3HX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01T75unqYuVfL8iKPmHn8kMi","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/chrisarter/Documents/projects/policy-engine/.claude/agent-memory/laravel-eloquent-expert/MEMORY.md","old_string":"## Key Files\n- `/src/PolicyEngineServiceProvider.php` - Merges config, publishes under `policy-engine-config` tag\n- `/config/policy-engine.php` - cache, protect_system_roles, log_denials, explain, document_format\n- `/phpunit.xml` - Feature test suite only, source coverage on `src/`","new_string":"## Database Schema (5 tables)\n- `permissions` - string PK (`id`), nullable `description`, timestamps\n- `roles` - string PK (`id`), `name`, `is_system` bool, timestamps\n- `role_permissions` - composite PK (`role_id`, `permission_id`), FK to roles cascade delete\n- `assignments` - auto-increment PK, polymorphic `subject`, `role_id` FK, nullable `scope`, unique constraint on all four, scope index\n- `boundaries` - auto-increment PK, unique `scope`, JSON `max_permissions`, timestamps\n- Migrations in `database/migrations/` using anonymous classes, no date prefix\n- Service provider loads migrations via `loadMigrationsFrom()` and publishes via `publishesMigrations()` with tag `policy-engine-migrations`\n\n## Key Files\n- `/src/PolicyEngineServiceProvider.php` - Merges config, loads migrations, publishes config (`policy-engine-config`) and migrations (`policy-engine-migrations`)\n- `/config/policy-engine.php` - cache, protect_system_roles, log_denials, explain, document_format\n- `/phpunit.xml` - Feature test suite only, source coverage on `src/`\n\n## Pint Style Notes\n- Uses `concat_space` fixer (no spaces around `.` concatenation operator)"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":616,"cache_read_input_tokens":29955,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":616},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01QthMt2vfnYoL6TihTPiTjx","session_id":"ce4d2e8c-11e0-48e3-8ef5-8ea123e4d07a","uuid":"09f06e8c-b3c8-4840-b88c-d292a5abe5e1"}
